# Setup Guide

## Clone repository
1) git clone https://github.com/Incognito0989/MAGGIE.git

## Install python

1) install python 3.12 onto server from python page
2) install pip from download page
3) tkinter may need to be separately installed

## Create/Activate python environment
1) go to MAGGIE directory
2) python3 -m venv venv
3) source venv/bin/activate

## Install dependencies
1) pip install -r requirements.txt

## Create desktop shortcut
1) move maggie.desktop to ~/Desktop directory
2) NOTE that directory of shorcut may need to be modified using vi to point to the tool

## Configure settings
1) settings.py can be configured with text editor or vim
   - configure the necessary settings to comply with the workflow

